# CI-ephemeral vendored/stub subcharts. .github/scripts/stub_missing_deps.py
# copies the real local subchart (e.g. charts/szl-receipts) and drops
# template-less placeholders for staged subcharts into <umbrella>/charts/ before
# rendering. These must NEVER be committed — Helm would then treat the snapshot
# as the source of truth and the umbrella would drift / go stale.
charts/*/charts/
